===Etymology===
Possibly Sino-Tibetan. According to {{zh-ref|Zhang, Jacques and Lai (2019)}}, the modern meaning of the word originated from a semantic narrowing of its original sense "to break", thus making it cognate with {{cog|sit-sit|ka-prāt|t=to break}} and also {{cog|sit-jap|prɤt|t=to break}}. Their common root would be {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*prat|t=to break}}.

