===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[lose]] (a game); to be [[defeated]]
#: {{zh-x|甲 隊 以 一 比 二 敗 於 乙 隊。|}}
#* {{zh-x|故 善戰 者，立 于 不敗 之 地，而 不失 敵 之 敗 也。|Hence the skillful fighter puts himself into a position which makes defeat impossible, and does not miss the moment for defeating the enemy.|ref=Sunzi}}
# to [[fail]]
#: {{zh-x|成敗|success or failure}}
# {{lb|zh|transitive}} to [[defeat]]
#* {{zh-x|六月，壬戌，公 敗 ^宋 師 于 ^菅。|In the sixth month, on [the day] Renxu, the duke '''defeated''' an army of Song at Jian.|ref=Zuozhuan-L}}
#* {{zh-x|冬，與 ^越 人 水戰，大敗 ^越 人，裂 地 而 封 之。|In the winter he had an engagement with that of Yue, on which he '''inflicted a great defeat''', and was invested with a portion of territory taken from Yue.|ref=Zhuangzi}}
# to [[tarnish]]; to [[ruin]]; to [[destroy]]
#: {{zh-x|敗家|to squander a family fortune}}
#: {{zh-x|身敗名裂|to have one's reputation destroyed}}
#: {{zh-x|傷風敗俗|to corrupt public morals}}
#* {{zh-x|若之何 其 以 病，敗 君 之 大事 也。||ref=Zuozhuan}}
# to [[wither]] and [[fall]]
#: {{zh-x|枯枝敗葉|withered branches and leaves}}
#: {{zh-x|菊花 敗 了。|The chrysanthemums have withered.}}
# [[dilapidated]]; [[worn-out]]; {{lb|zh|of clothing}} [[tattered]]
#: {{zh-x|敗絮|worn cotton wool}}
# to [[rot]]; [[rotten]]
#* {{zh-x|魚 餒 而 肉 敗 不 食。||ref=Analects}}
# to [[remove]]; to [[get rid of]]
#: {{zh-x|敗火|to relieve internal heat}}

